OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe PSNI has apologised for
OL,8,F"unacceptable failings" in their
OL,9,Finvestigation into the death of
OL,10,Fshowjumper Katie Simpson after a
OL,11,Freview found that "institutional
OL,12,Fmisogyny" contributed to "clear
OL,13,Fwarning signs" being missed.
OL,15,FThe independent review led by Dr Jan
OL,16,FMelia, commissioned by the Department
OL,17,Fof Justice, found that "not one
OL,18,Fofficer thought seriously about abuse/
OL,19,Fcontrol" in the police investigation
OL,20,Fin 2020.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@WO]sD@SOUtD@IO]tD@ZOUuD@NO]yD@
OL,26,AXOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FIt cited "systematic failures" and
OL,8,Falso criticised other bodies,
OL,9,Fincluding social services and the
OL,10,Fhealth service, over safeguarding, as
OL,11,Fwell as within the equestrian sector.
OL,13,FIt has made 16 recommendations, with
OL,14,Fmany focused on training.
OL,16,FPSNI Assistant Chief Constable Davy
OL,17,FBeck said the force accepts the
OL,18,Ffindings in full and their
OL,19,F"unacceptable failings" outlined
OL,20,Ftherein.
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@^O]{D@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"The review makes clear that we missed
OL,8,Fopportunities.
OL,10,F"Warning signs were not fully
OL,11,Frecognised early enough and we did not
OL,12,Flisten to some of those who raised
OL,13,Fearly concerns," he said.
OL,15,FHe added: "The failings are clear, we
OL,16,Ffell short and for that I am truly
OL,17,Fsorry."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUuD@PO]wD@KOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
