OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FMs Simpson, 21, from Tynan, Co Armagh,
OL,8,Fdied in Altnagelvin Area Hospital
OL,9,Falmost a week after an incident in
OL,10,FGortnessy Meadows, Lettershandoney.
OL,12,FPolice originally thought she had
OL,13,Ftaken her own life.
OL,15,FIt was not until the following year
OL,16,Fthat Jonathan Creswell, the partner of
OL,17,FMs Simpson's sister, was arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe trial of Creswell, 36, for the
OL,8,Fmurder of Ms Simpson ended in April
OL,9,F2024 after he took his own life
OL,10,Ffollowing the first day of proceedings.
OL,12,FThe report found that 37 people, both
OL,13,Ffemale and male, have come forward to
OL,14,Fsay they were abused by Creswell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FIt found officers failed to identify
OL,8,Finconsistencies in Creswell's account,
OL,9,Fneglected to preserve vital evidence,
OL,10,Foverlooked forensic scenes and
OL,11,Fopportunities, dismissed key witness
OL,12,Fstatements and failed to secure/
OL,13,Fexamine crucial digital communications
OL,14,Fsuch as text messages and phone
OL,15,Frecords that might have revealed
OL,16,Fpatterns of abuse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FIt went on to find that police
OL,8,Fofficers demonstrated a striking lack
OL,9,Fof professional curiosity, failed to
OL,10,Femploy an investigative mindset or
OL,11,Fconsider the possibility of abuse/
OL,12,Fcontrol, in spite of clear warning
OL,13,Fsigns.
OL,15,FMs Simpson had been going to a horse
OL,16,Fyard close to her home in Tynan from
OL,17,Fthe age of eight up to three times a
OL,18,Fweek to ride and care for horses.
OL,20,FCreswell worked at that yard and was
OL,21,Fdating her sister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe review report found that Creswell
OL,8,Fhad groomed her from the age of 10,
OL,9,Fsubjecting her to a "brutal regime of
OL,10,Fgrooming, coercive control, verbal
OL,11,Fdegradation and physical abuse".
OL,13,FThe report found the grooming and
OL,14,Fabusive behaviour was concealed behind
OL,15,Fa "charming facade".
OL,26,@qD@UOUsD@_O]wD@COUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe report examined 16 hospital visits
OL,8,Fby Ms Simpson between 2003 and 2020
OL,9,Fwith increasingly severe injuries,
OL,10,Fwhich were explained as being due to
OL,11,Fhorse riding, and found the pattern
OL,12,Fshould have prompted closer
OL,13,Fexamination.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, Creswell was found to have
OL,16,Fhad a long-term pattern of persistent
OL,17,Fand escalating offending that included
OL,18,Fmotoring offences, dangerous driving,
OL,19,Fanimal abuse, indecent exposure,
OL,20,Fsuspected fraud and domestic abuse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FPreviously, a Police Ombudsman report
OL,8,Fconcluded the initial police
OL,9,Finvestigation into Ms Simpson's death
OL,10,Fwas "flawed" and "failed the Simpson
OL,11,Ffamily".
OL,13,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,14,F(PSNI) apologised to Ms Simpson's
OL,15,Ffamily in 2024.
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@LO]rD@ROUsD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe independent review found a series
OL,8,Fof failings, from failing to treat her
OL,9,Fdeath as suspicious, deficiencies in
OL,10,Fscene management, neglect of forensic
OL,11,Fevidence, oversight of suspect
OL,12,Fhistory, inadequate witness strategy,
OL,13,Ffragmented leadership and
OL,14,Faccountability and limited
OL,15,Fdisciplinary action for the officers
OL,16,Fidentified for misconduct.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe review also found discrepancies in
OL,8,Finformation given by Creswell, a lack
OL,9,Fof investigation into evidence given
OL,10,Fby members of the public and poor
OL,11,Fcommunication with Ms Simpson's family.
OL,13,FIt also found "institutional
OL,14,Fmisogyny", with examples given of
OL,15,Freferring to Creswell as a "bad boy"
OL,16,Frather than "acknowledging him as a
OL,17,Fviolent perpetrator".
OL,26,@uD@OOUvD@IO]wD@\OUwD@dO]xD@MOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe review concluded this choice of
OL,8,Flanguage "trivialises male aggression,
OL,9,Fdismissing harmful behaviour and
OL,10,Fultimately protects male perpetrators,
OL,11,Fsimultaneously undermining the
OL,12,Fcredibility of female victims".
OL,14,F"Seeing this kind of language use by
OL,15,Fpolice, draws attention to the
OL,16,Fconcerns raised in the Angiolini
OL,17,FReview and highlights how
OL,18,Finstitutional cultures and
OL,19,Fcommunication practices perpetuate
OL,20,Fmisogyny," it found.
OL,26,@pD@JOUtD@^O]vD@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"There is no doubt that this kind of
OL,8,Flanguage is normalised, seen as a bit
OL,9,Fof laugh or banter, but this is part
OL,10,Fof the problem.
OL,12,F"Euphemistic or dismissive language,
OL,13,Fsuch as referring to a perpetrator as
OL,14,Fa 'bad boy' obscures the harm done by
OL,15,Fmen like Creswell, denying women's
OL,16,Fexperience of abuse."
OL,18,FIt continued: "The use of this kind of
OL,19,Flanguage is misogynistic because it
OL,20,Fprotects male perpetrators at the
OL,21,Fexpense of female victims.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@UO]zD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"Creswell's misogyny was a risk factor
OL,8,Ffor both women and for others who have
OL,9,Fcome forward because of this case.
OL,11,F"When police endorse misogyny, as they
OL,12,Fdo here, risk to women escalates.
OL,14,F"Institutional misogyny reinforces
OL,15,Frisk, allowing it to be minimised; it
OL,16,Fdismisses women's experiences,
OL,17,Fcreating and sustaining a culture
OL,18,Fwhere female victims are disbelieved,
OL,19,Fand perpetrators are given credibility
OL,20,Fand power.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,F"This was precisely the case for
OL,8,FKatie: not one officer thought
OL,9,Fseriously about abuse/control.
OL,11,F"Katie's lived experience was
OL,12,Fdisregarded, clear warning signs were
OL,13,Fignored, established protocols were
OL,14,Ftreated as optional/discretionary, and
OL,15,Fpolice chose to privilege Creswell's
OL,16,Faccount."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FIt found an "urgent need for trauma-
OL,8,Finformed training, gender-sensitive
OL,9,Frisk assessment, and a cultural shift
OL,10,Fwithin the PSNI, that challenges and
OL,11,Fchanges its own institutional
OL,12,Fmisogyny".
OL,14,FIn a foreword to the review's report,
OL,15,FMs Simpson's mother, Noeleen Mullan,
OL,16,Fsaid it had been "hard to read",
OL,17,Fnoting "so many things were missed,
OL,18,Fnot done properly and it felt like
OL,19,Fthere was a "lack of care for Katie
OL,20,Ffrom the police".
OL,26,@oD@MOUtD@IO]xD@ROUxD@_O]yD@HOU{D@MOU|D@
OL,26,APO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30618
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FChairman of the policing board Brendan
OL,8,FMullan said the review "sets out in
OL,9,Fstark detail a series of missed
OL,10,Fopportunities which makes for deeply
OL,11,Ftroubling reading" and highlights the
OL,12,Fneed for "both systems and attitudinal
OL,13,Fchange within policing and the
OL,14,FCriminal Justice System".
OL,16,FMaking an oral statement in the
OL,17,FAssembly, Justice Minister Naomi Long
OL,18,Fsaid a "debt of gratitude" was owed to
OL,19,Fall who raised concerns about the
OL,20,Fcircumstances surrounding the death of
OL,21,FMs Simpson.
OL,26,@pD@XOUsD@RO]tD@JOUvD@XO]zD@HOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30619
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FShe said the independent review "makes
OL,8,Ffor uncomfortable reading" and
OL,9,Fannounced that Dr Melia will co-
OL,10,Fordinate and chair an implementation
OL,11,Fgroup for the 16 recommendations.
OL,13,F"My department and our partners will
OL,14,Fact on the recommendations contained
OL,15,Fin Dr Melia's report and ensure
OL,16,Flessons are not simply learned but
OL,17,Fembedded," she told MLAs.
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@ZO]uD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30620
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778033004
OL,3,CPSNI apologises for 'unacceptable
OL,4,Cfailings' in Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FThe Katie Trust, set up in Ms
OL,8,FSimpson's memory, welcomed the review
OL,9,Fas representing a "significant and
OL,10,Fnecessary step toward transparency and
OL,11,Faccountability".
OL,26,@qD@SOUsD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/20
